-- W.House confident new drilling ban will stand up in court
-- 
-- Mon Jul 12, 2010 3:57pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2010/07/12/us-oil-spill-moratorium-whitehouse-idUSTRE66B5AV20100712

 

 WASHINGTON  (Reuters) - The White House is confident that its revised moratorium on offshore deepwater drilling, due to be released later on Monday, will stand up in court, spokesman Robert Gibbs said. 

 (Editing by  Sandra Maler )